### Add a new Post
POST http://localhost:3000/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "sender": "Revital",
    "title": "My first post",
    "content": "This is my first post"
}

### Get all posts

GET http://localhost:3000/posts

### Get a post by id

GET http://localhost:3000/posts/673b88268b2acc78014e1693

### Get posts by sender

GET http://localhost:3000/posts?sender=Revital


### Update a post

PUT http://localhost:3000/posts/673b88268b2acc78014e1693
Content-Type: application/json

